embeddedItem.name: "Exquisite Ingenuity"
embeddedItem.desc:
A record that can be played on the Express' phonograph. It might be a chance acquisition or a gift from someone else. All sorts of memories surge up when the music plays — the smiles, encounters, touches, and the excitement of battle. Maybe that is why people still collect records even as society rapidly advances.
The current record contains the track, "Exquisite Ingenuity."
embeddedItem.lore: By measuring, the load-bearing of starskiffs derived. By examination, the quality of material determined. Meticulously, detailed blueprints drafted. Meticulously followed, exquisite delves constructed.
